	dprr:hasNoteText "A senator in the 70s. Varro Menipp. 453 B (from Nonius 199 L); but the best MS reading may be Attius. He may perhaps be identified with C. Attius Celsus (MRR 2.157-158). See Wiseman NM 216, no. 87.\n" .
